Hi Folks,

 

See below email, it seems they require some assistance to be able to read
their utility meters.

 

Please advise how you want to proceed.

 



 

 

 

From: Kgotodia Hloaisi <kgotodia@hotmail.com> 
Sent: Monday, February 25, 2019 10:33 PM
To: Antonio Sierra <antonio@sectionalts.co.za>
Cc: masellor62@gmail.com; makhooanepali@gmail.com; Craig
<craig@sectionalts.co.za>
Subject: BC METER READINGS MONTHLY

 

Hi Antonio

 

Kindly take note, after numerous attempt in response to the above request we
find it difficult to read the meters.

 

Our main problem is that, we are unable to reach  meters because of their
conditions, i.e liking and full of mortar all over. We have tried to contact
Metsi  a Lekoa which a water division of Emfuleni Municipality at this
numbers : 016 986 8361 with any result. We find it difficult to understand,
how do they bill us under the conditions.

For your attention and further handling please.

 

We wish to advice you that if this can be addressed, it is not a problem for
us to read the meters.

 

Kind regards

Kgotodia

 

 

 

 

 

  _____  

From: Antonio Sierra <antonio@sectionalts.co.za
<mailto:antonio@sectionalts.co.za> >
Sent: Friday, 25 January 2019 2:05 PM
To: 'Kgotodia Hloaisi'; masellor62@gmail.com <mailto:masellor62@gmail.com> ;
makhooanepali@gmail.com <mailto:makhooanepali@gmail.com> 
Subject: RE: BANKING DEVELOPMENTS AND MONTHLY INCOME AND EXPENDITURE 

 

Hi Kgotodia,

 

Compliments for the new year, may it be a great year.

 

I just want to confirm if it is possible for someone to do the BC meter
readings monthly, including the municipal bulk meter.

 



 

 


